headline.print_headline: Nurse Who Fought Maine Ebola Quarantine Moving Out of State: Report
headline.main: Nurse Who Fought Ebola Quarantine Said to Be Leaving Maine

lead_paragraph: Kaci Hickox and her boyfriend have decided to move from her home state, he told The Press Herald newspaper, but would not say where.
